<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" sizes="16x16" href="https://www.stib-mivb.be/irj/go/km/docs/WEBSITE_RES/Webresources/Frontend/build/images/favicon.ico">
    <title><%= title %></title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-MCw98/SFnGE8fJT3GXwEOngsV7Zt27NXFoaoApmYm81iuXoPkFOJwJ8ERdknLPMO" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: stibIcons;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: normal;
            src: url(/fonts/stibIcons.woff) format("woff"), url(/fonts/stibIcons.ttf) format("truetype")
        }

        @font-face {
            font-family: Brusseline;
            font-weight: 400;
            font-style: normal;
            src: url(/fonts/brusseline-webfont.woff) format("woff"), url(/fonts/brusseline-webfont.ttf) format("truetype")
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 .2em;
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #d62027;
            font-family: TradeGothic, Brusseline, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h2 {
            margin: 0 0 .2em;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #0077c1;
            font-family: TradeGothic, Brusseline, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        h2:before {
            font-family: stibIcons;
            content: "";
        }

        /* ========== Navbar ========== */
        /* ----- Global ------ */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, white 22%, #02538a 22%);
        }

        ul {
            position: -webkit-sticky; /* Safari */
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            /*background-color: #02538a;*/
            /* Flex part */
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-end;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            flex-direction: row;
        }

        li {
            float: left;
            transform: skewX(-5deg);
        }

        li a {
            display: block;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            text-decoration: none!important;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        li a.active {
            background-color: #085d96;
        }

        li a:hover {
            background-color: #0077c1;
            color: white;
        }

        /* ----- Éléments personalisés ------ */
        .navigation_title, .header img {
            transform: skewX(5deg);
            margin: 0;
        }

        li:first-child {
            background-color: white;
        }

        li:first-child a:hover {
            background-color: white;
        }

        .header ul li>a span[class^=icon-] {
            padding: 0 0.5rem;
        }

        .icon-plan:before {
            font-family: stibIcons;
            content:"";
        }

        /* ========== Title division ========== */
        .title_division {
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }
        
        .title_division img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 150px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        
        .title_division h1 {
            position: absolute;
            top: 34%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .title_division h2 {
            position: absolute;
            top: 55%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 100%;
        }

        /* ========== Table ========== */
        .table .thead-light th {
            color: #495057;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border-color: #e8e8e8;
        }

        .table-hover tbody tr:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.02);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <ul class="container">
            <li>
                <a href="/">
                    <img src="https://www.stib-mivb.be/irj/go/km/docs/WEBSITE_RES/Webresources/Frontend/build/images/logo.svg" alt="Homepage">
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/" class="active">
                    <p class="navigation_title"><span class="icon-plan" area-hidden="true"></span>Home</p>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/">
                    <p class="navigation_title"><span class="icon-plan" area-hidden="true"></span>Vehicle position</p>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/">
                    <p class="navigation_title"><span class="icon-plan" area-hidden="true"></span>Waiting time</p>
                </a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="/">
                    <p class="navigation_title"><span class="icon-plan" area-hidden="true"></span>Connect</p>
                </a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </header>

    <div class="title_division">
        <img src="https://www.stib-mivb.be/irj/go/km/docs/WEBSITE_RES/Webresources/Frontend/build/images/pattern-white.png">
        <h1 class="container"><%= title %></h1>
        <h2 class="container"><%= subtitle %></h2>
    </div>

    <main class="container">
        <p>Les données de l'API STIB sur la position en temps réel des véhicules sont juste ici !</p>

        <table class="table table-hover">
            <thead class="thead-light">
                <tr>
                    <th scope="col">#</th>
                    <th scope="col">Line</th>
                    <th scope="col">Vehicle positions</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <% mongoData.forEach((item, index) => { %>
                    <tr>
                        <th scope="row"><%= index + 1 %></th>
                        <td><%= item.lineid %></td>
                        <td><%= item.vehiclepositions %></td>
                    </tr>
                <% }); %>
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
